Welcome to my show! Its the only Galactic Game Show with  lives  on
the line! Some of you silly humans describe it as Twin-stick, Deck-
building, and Rogue-lite - whatever that means. Fail  but  prevail!
My show is known  for its  tense moments  and  spectacular  deaths.
Quick  reactions  are  important  -  but  so is  a  good  strategy.
Contestants who learn from their deaths, tend not to repeat them.
